#: ../../../release_details/9.5/qml-multitouch.md:1
msgid "Multi-touch gestures in QtQuick/QML"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/qml-multitouch.md:3
msgid ""
"Added support multi-touch interaction to `QQuickVTKItem` using the "
"[PinchHandler](https://doc.qt.io/qt-6/qml-qtquick-pinchhandler.html) QML "
"component. To attach the handler to a QQuickVTKItem, simply connect the new "
"slots to the `[translation|rotation|scale]Changed` signals of the handler."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/qml-multitouch.md:8
msgid "Example usage"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/qml-multitouch.md:10
msgid ""
"\n"
"  QVTKItem{\n"
"    id: qvtkitem\n"
"    anchors.fill: parent\n"
"  }\n"
"\n"
"  PinchHandler {\n"
"    id: pch\n"
"    target: null\n"
"    onTranslationChanged: (delta) => qvtkitem.pinchHandlerTranslate(pch."
"centroid.position, delta)\n"
"    onScaleChanged: (delta) => qvtkitem.pinchHandlerScale(pch.centroid."
"position, delta)\n"
"    onRotationChanged: (delta) => qvtkitem.pinchHandlerRotate(pch.centroid."
"position, delta)\n"
"  }\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
